verbose_text: The antisense probes were determined to be specific as expression of transgenic RNAi against the transcript of interest abolished FISH signal (supplementary material Fig. S3B, F), while over-expression of the transcript of interest elevated FISH signal (supplementary material Fig. S3C, G).
